                <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100"><img  src="/badge-assets/{{$url['slug']}}/_global/img/analytics-social-mentions.svg" alt="" /><span>Social mentions</span>Social mentions are the social conversations that are taking place on social networks about your brand, company, industry, product(s) and/or service(s). Measuring the volume of social mentions matters to analyse trends and patterns when social conversations peaked and dropped. For example, you may want to count how often a particular word, phrase or sentence is mentioned on social networks over a given time period.</p></li>
